## 🏗️ BACKEND — `dashboard.py` Architecture

```
FastAPI App
│
├─ Lifespan event (startup/shutdown)
│       Khởi tạo DashboardHub (WebSocket manager)
│       Spawn background task: _queue_drain_loop()
│       Đọc dashboard_config.json
│
├─ ── REST ENDPOINTS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
│
├─ GET /
│       Render templates/index.html (Jinja2)
│
├─ GET /api/candles
│       Params: symbol, tf (M5/M15/H1), limit (default 500)
│       Logic: Đọc từ DataPipeline._data_store hoặc gọi MT5 
│              copy_rates_from_pos() nếu pipeline chưa có
│       Return: JSON array [{time, open, high, low, close, volume}, ...]
│               ← Format chuẩn cho LightweightCharts candleSeries.setData()
│
├─ GET /api/trades
│       Params: limit (default 50), status (open/closed/all)
│       Logic: Đọc data/trade_log.csv (viết bởi execution.py)
│       Return: JSON array [{ticket, direction, entry, sl, tp, pnl, ...}, ...]
│
├─ GET /api/status
│       Return: JSON {
│           bot_state: "IN_TRADE",
│           equity: 1023.45,
│           balance: 1000.00,
│           daily_drawdown_pct: 2.31,
│           open_trade: {ticket, direction, entry, sl, tp, floating_pnl},
│           safety_net: "active" | "cooldown" | "paused" | "halted",
│           last_signal_score: 0.71,
│           uptime_sec: 3600
│       }
│
├─ ── WEBSOCKET ENDPOINT ────────────────────────────────────────────────
│
├─ WS /ws
│       DashboardHub.connect(websocket)
│       Gửi ngay "snapshot" event (toàn bộ state hiện tại) sau khi connect
│       Loop: nhận ping/keepalive từ client
│       Cleanup: DashboardHub.disconnect(websocket) khi đóng
│
├─ ── INTERNAL ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
│
├─ DashboardHub  [WebSocket Manager]
│       connected: set[WebSocket]
│       async connect(ws) / disconnect(ws)
│       async broadcast(message: dict) → gửi JSON tới tất cả connected clients
│       (Bắt WebSocketDisconnect để tự dọn clients đã chết)
│
├─ DashboardPublisher  [Bridge sang main.py — THREAD-SAFE]
│       _queue: asyncio.Queue(maxsize=200)
│       publish(event: dict) → _queue.put_nowait(event)
│                              (Non-blocking — nếu full thì discard oldest)
│       _queue_drain_loop():  asyncio background task
│           while True:
│               event = await _queue.get()
│               await hub.broadcast(event)
│
└─ Singleton: dashboard_pub = DashboardPublisher()
              dashboard_hub = DashboardHub()
              Được import bởi main.py để gọi publish()
```

