## 📡 WEBSOCKET EVENT SCHEMA

Tất cả events gửi qua WS đều có format JSON chuẩn:

```json
{
  "type":      "<event_type>",
  "ts":        1741194000,
  "symbol":    "EURUSDc",
  "payload":   { ... }
}
```

### Danh sách Event Types:

| Type | Trigger trong main.py | Payload | Frontend Action |
|------|----------------------|---------|-----------------|
| `snapshot` | Khi WS client mới connect | full status object | Initial render toàn bộ UI |
| `candle_close` | `_state_idle()` sau khi nến M5 mới đóng | `{time, o, h, l, c, vol}` | `candleSeries.update()` |
| `state_change` | `_transition(new_state)` | `{old, new, ts}` | Update BotState badge + màu ring |
| `equity_update` | `_state_in_trade()` mỗi 0.5s | `{equity, balance, floating_pnl, dd_pct}` | Update Equity widget + DD gauge |
| `signal_found` | `_state_scanning()` khi signal | `{direction, score, fvg:{top,bot}, entry_price}` | Vẽ FVG box + entry line preview |
| `order_filled` | `_state_pending_order()` FILLED | `{ticket, direction, entry, sl, tp, lot}` | Vẽ Entry arrow + SL/TP horizontal lines |
| `trade_closed` | `_state_closing()` done | `{ticket, pnl, reason, close_price}` | Vẽ close marker + pnl badge trên chart |
| `safety_event` | `risk_manager._trigger_*()` | `{level, reason, resume_at}` | Flash warning banner |
| `fvg_detected` | `strategy_engine.analyze()` qua hub | `{direction, top, bot, age, quality}` | Vẽ FVG box (semi-transparent) |

