## 🎨 CHART OVERLAY — LightweightCharts API

Đây là phần TechLead và Sếp Vũ sẽ nhìn thấy nhiều nhất. Cần rõ ràng, đẹp, không rối:

```javascript
// Khởi tạo chart
const chart = LightweightCharts.createChart(document.getElementById('chart'), {
    layout: { background: {color: '#0d0f14'}, textColor: '#8892a4' },
    grid:   { vertLines: {color: '#1a1d26'}, horzLines: {color: '#1a1d26'} },
    crosshair: { mode: LightweightCharts.CrosshairMode.Normal },
    width:  document.getElementById('chart').clientWidth,
    height: 520,
});

const candleSeries = chart.addCandlestickSeries({
    upColor:   '#00d4a0', downColor:  '#ff4f6d',
    borderUpColor: '#00d4a0', borderDownColor: '#ff4f6d',
    wickUpColor:   '#00d4a0', wickDownColor:   '#ff4f6d',
});

// Khi nhận candle_close event qua WS:
// candleSeries.update({time, open, high, low, close});

// ── FVG Box ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Dùng chart.addHistogramSeries() hoặc Series với custom markers
// Alternatively: SVG overlay div absolute-positioned trên chart canvas

// ── SL / TP Lines ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
const slLine = chart.addLineSeries({
    color: '#ff4f6d', lineWidth: 1,
    lineStyle: LightweightCharts.LineStyle.Dashed,
    lastPriceAnimation: LightweightCharts.LastPriceAnimationMode.Disabled,
});
// slLine.setData([{time: entry_time, value: sl_price}, {time: now, value: sl_price}]);

// ── Entry Marker ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
candleSeries.setMarkers([{
    time:     entry_time,
    position: 'belowBar',  // BUY: below; SELL: above
    color:    '#00d4a0',
    shape:    'arrowUp',   // BUY arrow
    text:     `BUY @ ${entry_price}`,
}]);
```

